@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}


<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<p>
    Welcome to the Student Library Management System. We take the privacy of our users seriously and are committed to protecting your personal information.
</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<p>
    When using this system, we may collect personal information including your name, email address, student ID, and any other information necessary for managing your library account and processing book loans.
</p>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>
    The information collected is used solely for the purpose of managing your library account, including:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Tracking borrowed and returned books.</li>
    <li>Sending email notifications about overdue books or fines.</li>
    <li>Managing your book reservations and appointment history.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Protection</h2>
<p>
    We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure the security of your personal data. Your information is stored in a secure database and access is limited to authorized personnel only.
</p>

<h2>Third-Party Sharing</h2>
<p>
    We do not share your personal information with third parties unless required by law or necessary for the functionality of the system (e.g., email notifications).
</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>
<p>
    You have the right to access, modify, or delete your personal data at any time. For any requests related to your data, please contact the system administrator.
</p>

<h2>Changes to the Policy</h2>
<p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page, and we encourage you to review it periodically.
</p>

<p>
    If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, please contact us through the provided support channels.
</p>
